    "This helps in stimulating the generator to output more diversified images.",
    "DALLE-2 was introduced by OpenAI (Ramesh et al.",
    "2022; OpenAI 2022) as a text-to-image generative model that comprises two primary components: a prior that generates a CLIP image embedding based on a text caption and a decoder that creates an image conditioned on the image embedding.",
    "The imageto-text is the opposite of text-to-image, and it involves generating descriptive text from input images.",
    "Image captioning is a popular application of this technique."
